Package com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui.commands.handler

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AboutCommandCallback
    The interface AboutCommandCallback is a callback interface used to notify the integration that the about button in the main menu or toolbar was clicked.
    HelpCommandCallback
    The interface HelpCommandCallback is a callback interface used to notify the integration that the help button in the main menu or toolbar was clicked.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutCommandClickHandler
    The AboutCommandClickHandler shows the about dialog via AboutCommandCallback.
    CheckWithCorrectionDialogClickHandler
    The class CheckWithCorrectionDialogClickHandler is the ClickHandler for the CheckWithCorrectionDialogCommand.
    ContributeTermCommandClickHandler
    The class ContributeTermCommandClickHandler is the ClickHandler for the ContributeTermCommand.
    DefaultAboutCommandCallback
    The DefaultAboutCommandCallback is a small default implementation opening a small message box with about information.
    FlagHelpCommandClickHandler
    The class FlagHelpCommandClickHandler is the ClickHandler of the flag help command created by ContextMenuCommandFactory.createHelpCommand(String, boolean, boolean, Flag, WebPagePresenter, java.net.URL, com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui.dialogs.callbacks.Listener) .
    FlagLocalHelpCommandClickHandler
    The class FlagLocalHelpCommandClickHandler is the ClickHandler of the flag help command created by ContextMenuCommandFactory.createLocalHelpCommand(String, boolean, boolean, Flag, WebPagePresenter, java.net.URL, com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui.dialogs.callbacks.Listener) .
    GuiControllerCallbackFactory
    A factory for creating the DefaultAboutCommandCallback.
